TechnologyOne Sub-Processors
The
TechnologyOne Sub-Processors webpage
provides information on the sub-processors that we engage to provide processing activities on customer data on behalf of customers. Prior to engaging any third-party sub-processor, TechnologyOne undertakes diligence to evaluate their privacy, security and confidentiality practices, and executes an agreement including the required obligations under privacy law. All sub-processor arrangements follow the written agreements we have in place with our customers.
